metadata.description: For One of None's NFT.NYC 2022 Hybrid Gallery event, a select number of Vault Club Creators and Collectors will be invited to collect the "Founding Member" jacket. In continuation of its initial hoodie series, One of None has created its 2022 signature piece. These jackets will be released as fully hybrid NFTs and will be numbered 1 to 100.
metadata.name: Jacket - 1/100
